<p>While actress Sadie, 55, wrote: 'Happy 18th birthday to my beautiful god daughter <?php echo e('@'); ?>lilamoss... what an amazing young lady you are - so very proud, sassy and smart and so very beautiful... big kiss baby girl.. love from the whole fam <?php echo e('@'); ?>irislaw.'</p>

<p>Alongside the touching message Sadie also shared a throwback snap of Lila and her daughter Iris, 19. On her Instagram Stories the star shared a further picture of Lila and Iris together as young girls.</p>

