<p>Kate returned to London last month after she had been isolating in her Cotswolds mansion with Lila alongside her long-term partner Count Nikolai and her half-sister Lottie, 22. </p>

<p>Elegant: Kate made a typically stylish arrival</p>

<p>The troupe were also joined by Kate's hairdresser friend James Brown.</p>

